THIRD PARTY DATA AND SERVICES

This software uses data and services from third parties:

1. Seoul Open Data Portal (서울시 공공데이터 포탈)
   - Website: https://data.seoul.go.kr/
   - Data used: Real-time city data, air quality, bike sharing status, cultural events
   - License: Seoul Open Data Portal Terms of Use
   - Attribution: Data provided by Seoul Metropolitan Government
   
   The data from Seoul Open Data Portal is subject to their terms of use.
   Users of this software must comply with Seoul Open Data Portal's licensing
   terms when using or redistributing this data.

2. External APIs
   - Weather data APIs
   - Public transportation APIs
   - Cultural event APIs
   
   Each external API may have its own terms of service and licensing requirements.
   Users are responsible for complying with these terms when using this software.

DISCLAIMER: This software is not affiliated with or endorsed by Seoul Metropolitan
Government or any of the data providers mentioned above.
